question:
What will be the output if num = -5 in the following code?

if num > 0:
    print("Positive")
else:
    print("Negative")

What will be the output of the following code if num = 0?

if num > 0:
    print("Positive")
elif num < 0:
    print("Negative")
else:
    print("Zero")

What will be the output of the following age verification program if the user inputs 17?

age = int(input("Enter your age: "))
if age >= 18:
    print("You are eligible to vote.")
else:
    print("Sorry, you must be at least 18 years old to vote.")
